{"type":"message","id":"24d774ce","parentId":"f0e53bbd","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:50:53.586Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到已经有一个每日推送claudecode的定时任务，用户现在需要增加一个cursor相关的定时任务。我需要创建一个新的cron job，同样每天运行，推送cursor相关的动态。按照要求，sessionTarget是isolated，payload是agentTurn，delivery是announce到用户。\n\n现在我来构造job对象：名称是\"每日推送cursor相关动态\"，schedule是每天9点10分（错开claudecode的推送），expr是\"10 9 * * *\"，tz是Asia/Shanghai，payload里的message是获取最新cursor相关的最热动态，包括github热门项目、最新工具发布、相关新闻资讯、插件推荐等，整理成清晰内容推送给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_phxtpqtjl22395nrjllz2euk","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"每日推送cursor相关动态","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"10 9 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请帮我获取最新cursor编辑器相关的最热动态，包括github热门项目、最新工具发布、相关新闻资讯、优秀插件推荐、使用技巧分享，整理成清晰的内容推送给用户ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25","timeoutSeconds":300},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","to":"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25","channel":"feishu"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","enabled":true}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":974,"output":404,"cacheRead":34104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35482,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775706645277}}
